Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.92,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hallo und herzlich willkommen!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.92,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hello and welcome!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.66,0:00:07.20,Transcription,,0,0,0,,In dieser kleinen Präsentation möchte ich euch Whispersub
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.66,0:00:07.20,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,In this small presentation I would like to introduce you to Whispersub
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.82,Transcription,,0,0,0,,vorstellen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.82,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.56,0:00:13.88,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Mit diesem Tool könnt ihr Audiospuren aus MKV-Dateien extrahieren,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.56,0:00:13.88,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,With this tool you can extract audio tracks from MKV files,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.18,Transcription,,0,0,0,,automatisch transkribieren
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.18,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,automatically transcribe them
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.52,Transcription,,0,0,0,,und mit bestehenden Untertiteln zusammenführen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.52,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,and merge them with existing subtitles.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.64,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Besonders praktisch ist, dass verschiedene
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.64,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,Particularly practical is that different
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.96,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Sprachen unterstützt werden und eine
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.96,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,languages are supported and
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.68,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Romanisierung in lateinische Schrift möglich ist.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.68,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,romanization into Latin script is possible.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.46,0:00:28.68,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Auch
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.46,0:00:28.68,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,Even
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.88,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hintergrundgeräusche stellen kein großes Problem dar.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.88,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,background noise is not a major problem.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.38,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Denn Whispersub kann Stimmen
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.38,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,Because Whispersub can separate voices
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.38,Transcription,,0,0,0,,von der restlichen Tonspur trennen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.38,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,from the rest of the audio track.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.98,Transcription,,0,0,0,,So wird die Erstellung präziser und übersichtlicher
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.98,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,This makes the creation of precise and clear
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.10,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Untertitel deutlich einfacher.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.10,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,subtitles much easier.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.98,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Probiert es gerne selbst aus!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.98,Default_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,Feel free to try it out yourself!
